I had to use two different methods for the pre-GHC-7.10 versions and the post, with the caveat that 8.4.4 doesn't work on the 'new' method. The tool `haskell-ci` just generated a file for me that left out the 9.x versions, even though I asked for them in the .cabal file :shrug:
